WEBVTT

00:07.059 --> 00:09.989
I'm getting pretty good at this parallel parking.

00:10.128 --> 00:12.029
That's not what this is, but okay.

00:15.453 --> 00:18.837
You know, it was fun sightseeing with you.

00:18.920 --> 00:20.679
How'd you know where all those celebrities lived?

00:20.828 --> 00:22.687
I've done some light stalking in my day.

00:24.608 --> 00:26.718
Ugh, look at this poor guy.

00:26.886 --> 00:28.745
He's got, like, ten tickets and a boot.

00:28.858 --> 00:30.991
I've seen this car. It's been here for like a month.

00:31.079 --> 00:32.375
Who leaves their car like this?

00:32.438 --> 00:34.097
Well, whoever he is, he's a big fan of mine.

00:34.151 --> 00:36.310
He's got a stack of my headshots in the front seat.

00:37.369 --> 00:40.365
Joey, when you bought your new car, you did return the rental, right?

